Originally from http://www.gpucomputing.net/?q=node/1314
Adapted by Ben Shelton

Build with "nvcc -arch=sm_21 BurtscherGCG.2.1.cu"

Run with "./a.out 16384 1000 system16384.dat 1"

where

Argument 1: number of bodies
Argument 2: number of iterations
Argument 3: data file
Argument 4: how often to send data back (1 is every iteration, 10 is every 10 iterations, etc.)

